      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRACE ILE (4) goes very well over this trip including five wins. Placed last time (30.17) at Q Parklands in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten a neck. Looks the one to beat with even luck. HARA'S OTIS (2) has been out of the placings last two but shapes well for this if he can recapture his sharp win a few runs back, getting around this track over 457m in 25.37. Should be in this for a long way. BY A MIRACLE (1) pinged the lids last start from an awkward draw and led throughout to score (19.13) at Q Straight in a Mix 5 over 350m. Should feature again. HOLD THE GAVEL (8) won as punters' elect last time – sure to feature again.",
